*Marshal of Poland
*General field marshal (Imperial Russia)
*Marshal of the Russian Federation
*Marshal of the Soviet Union
*Fältmarskalk (Sweden)
*Chom phon (Thailand)
*Gensui (Imperial Japanese Army)

