<doc id="200371" wikidata="Q6844248" url="?curid=200371" title="Mignano Gap">
<text>The Mignano Gap is a geographic feature in Italy, in the vicinity of Mignano Monte Lungo. During World War II, this was the location of the German Bernhardt Line.

